r shear in the emission wavelength is\nseen. A plausible explanation for the line profile is that the emission gas is\nexpelled from C15 in a bipolar outflow, similar to that seen in M82.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Feb 2004 09:39:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
